{"type":null,"faqId":40444,"title":"如何修改 Wi-Fi 的 11n 频宽？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>路由器频宽是调制载波占据的频率范围，也是发送无线信号频率的标准。20MHz在11n的情况下能达到144Mbps带宽，它穿透性较好，传输距离远；40MHz在802.11n的情况下能达到300Mbps带宽，但穿透性稍差，传输距离近，容易产生干扰，影响网络传输。因此，如果为了获得更大的传输速度，可以选用40MHz。但是在应用环境中，无线信号较多的话，则不建议选择40MHz了，否则任意使用1到6信道的无线信号都会干扰40MHz频宽的通讯。建议您使用路由器默认的20/40MHz混合模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>登录路由器Web配置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s2\">更多功能 &gt;</span><span> </span><span class=\"s2\">Wi-Fi 设置 &gt; Wi-Fi 高级</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">2.4G Wi-Fi</span><span>”区域的“</span><span class=\"s2\">Wi-Fi 频宽设置</span><span>”中，选择想要设置的频宽。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s2\">保存</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137275\" style=\"width:5.507639in;height:6.3541665in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5791","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0"